reviews.text: 唔錯😋
呢間以同區來講價錢比較偏貴，連早餐都貴過其他餐聽一成,至於口味嘅野就見人見智。
食物質素一般，“奶油脆豬”俾隔夜麵包製成，伙記服務態度強差人意，有時侯把口給說話客人聽，讓人感覺不舒服
食過末炒牛河，奶茶，沒有什麼特式，電視介紹過我覺得一般。
多款式食品，冰室最特色食品都算是即場當面燒的干炒牛河，環境舒適。

reviews.text: Nice MTR station same as other MTR stations in Hong Kong. Nicely managed crowd system for peak hours. Very helpful staff. Quick access to exits. Easy and fast access using octopus cards. Good facility for wheel chair and strollers. Thanks to MTR staff and management for making the journey healthy and quick.
One of the MTR stations in New Territories full of interesting local restaurants offering Hong Kong style cuisines and Cantonese Cuisine.
nice place for kids to play
becoming very different. lots of restaurants. learning centers for kids and all kinds of shops.
Good place change a lot I visit there after 4 years
冇人理會，好像在家一樣，自己照顧自己 如想快趣有嘢食就拎張點心紙去搵服務員 唔搵佢大半個鐘頭都唔會行埋嚟
去石門午飯，晚飯都很方便。
新開的 [SUPINE]西餐廳 ，好正！

石門站（英語：Shek Mun Station）是港鐵馬鞍山綫的一個架空車站，位於沙田區石門東南部安明街旁，並於2004年12月21日啟用。

樓層	
編輯
P		1號月台 馬鞍山綫往大圍（第一城）
島式月台，開左邊門
2號月台 馬鞍山綫往烏溪沙（大水坑）	
C	大堂	出入口、客務中心、商店、自助服務、洗手間

石門站設有7間商店，包括便利店、麵包糕餅店、零食專賣店等。站內亦設有不同銀行所提供的自動櫃員機[1]。

Nice MTR station same as other MTR stations in Hong Kong. Nicely managed crowd system for peak hours. Very helpful staff. Quick access to exits. Easy and fast access using octopus cards. Good facility for wheel chair and strollers. Thanks to MTR staff and management for making the journey healthy and quick.
